&ANALYZE-SUSPEND _UIB-CODE-BLOCK _PROCEDURE destroyObject Procedure 
PROCEDURE destroyObject :
/*------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  Purpose:     SmartDataBrowser version of destroyObject which lets its
